net.sf.mmm.util.lang.api.attribute

Interface AttributeReadMinimumValue<VALUE>

  • Type Parameters:
    VALUE - is the generic type of the minimum value. This is typically a Number but may potentially also be something else (e.g. a Date). Should be the same type as AttributeReadValue.getValue().
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AttributeWriteMinimumValue<VALUE>, NumberType<NUMBER>, Segment<V>, UiWidgetAdapterDoubleField, UiWidgetAdapterIntegerField, UiWidgetAdapterIntegerSliderField, UiWidgetAdapterLongField, UiWidgetAdapterNumberField<VALUE>, UiWidgetAdapterRangeField<VALUE>, UiWidgetDoubleField, UiWidgetIntegerField, UiWidgetIntegerSliderField, UiWidgetLongField, UiWidgetRangeField<VALUE>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDoubleSegment, AbstractSegment, AbstractUiWidgetDoubleField, AbstractUiWidgetIntegerField, AbstractUiWidgetIntegerSliderField, AbstractUiWidgetLongField, AbstractUiWidgetNumberField, AbstractUiWidgetRangeField, Alpha, Blue, Brightness, Chroma, ColorFactor, DoubleSpinBox, Factor, Green, Hue, IntegerRangeBox, IntegerSpinBox, Lightness, LongSpinBox, NumberBox, NumberSpinBox, NumberTypeImpl, Range, Red, Saturation, UiWidgetAdapterGwtCheckboxField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtColorField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtComboBoxField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtDateField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtDoubleField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtFieldFocusWidget, UiWidgetAdapterGwtFieldFocusWidgetBase, UiWidgetAdapterGwtFieldValueBox, UiWidgetAdapterGwtFieldValueBoxBase, UiWidgetAdapterGwtFileField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtIntegerField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtIntegerSliderField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtListBoxCombo, UiWidgetAdapterGwtLocalDateField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtLocalTimeField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtLongField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtNumberField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtPasswordField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtRadioButtons, UiWidgetAdapterGwtRadioButtonsHorizontal, UiWidgetAdapterGwtRadioButtonsVertical, UiWidgetAdapterGwtRichTextField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtTextAreaBase, UiWidgetAdapterGwtTextAreaField, UiWidgetAdapterGwtTextBoxBase, UiWidgetAdapterGwtTextField, UiWidgetAdapterTestDoubleField, UiWidgetAdapterTestIntegerField, UiWidgetAdapterTestLongField, UiWidgetAdapterTestNumberField, UiWidgetDoubleFieldGwt, UiWidgetDoubleFieldTestImpl, UiWidgetIntegerFieldGwt, UiWidgetIntegerFieldTestImpl, UiWidgetIntegerSliderFieldGwt, UiWidgetIntegerSliderFieldTestImpl, UiWidgetLongFieldGwt, UiWidgetLongFieldTestImpl

    public interface AttributeReadMinimumValue<VALUE>
    This interface gives read access to the minimum value attribute of an object.
    Since:
    4.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)

    • Method Detail

      • getMinimumValue

        VALUE getMinimumValue()
        This method gets the minimum value of this object. A legal value has to be greater or equal to this minimum.
        Returns:
        the minimum allowed for value or null if unbounded.
